com.chdryra.android.reviewer

Class ControllerReviewTreeEditable

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.chdryra.android.reviewer.ControllerReview<ReviewEditable>
      • com.chdryra.android.reviewer.ControllerReviewEditable
        • com.chdryra.android.reviewer.ControllerReviewTreeEditable

  •  class ControllerReviewTreeEditable
extends ControllerReviewEditable
    Controls editing of review trees in the android activities/fragments layer (the View layer in an MVC framework).

    Holds 2 objects:

    • Node controller: controls access to the review-in-progress node model
    • Collection of sub-review controllers: There maybe multiple controllers associated with the potential tree structure of the review in progress that may need to be passed back and forth between activities.

    See Also:
    ControllerReview, ControllerReviewNodeExpandable
